author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Initiator Pharma Raises About SEK 20.6 Million In Rights Issue
text:
April 5 (Reuters) - INITIATOR PHARMA A/S:
* THE RIGHTS ISSUE OF UNITS HAS BEEN OVERSUBSCRIBED * ‍ISSUE WAS SUBSCRIBED TO APPROXIMATELY SEK 20,6 MILLION, RESPONDING TO A SUBSCRIPTION RATE OF APPROXIMATELY 108 PERCENT​
* CONTRACT NOTES ARE PLANNED TO BE SENT OUT TODAY, ON APRIL 5TH, 2018.
* SINCE RIGHTS ISSUE WAS OVERSUBSCRIBED, SUBSCRIPTION GUARANTEES ARE NOT ACTIVATED Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
